      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材指出水与生命、日常生活和工农业生产密切相关，并引出水资源利用和天然水净化问题。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol1-knowledge-topic-0251-source-section-l3055-l3069-85b94ec8b9-promote-knowledge-topic-0251-source-section-l3055-l3069-85b94ec8b9-quiz-quiz-0251-source-section-l3055-l3069-85b94ec8b9",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材指出化学反应是原子重新组合生成新物质的过程，反应前后原子种类、数目和质量不变。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol1-knowledge-topic-0253-source-section-l3072-l3079-df771f9564-promote-knowledge-topic-0253-source-section-l3072-l3079-df771f9564-quiz-quiz-0253-source-section-l3072-l3079-df771f9564",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材说明质量守恒思想经历从朴素观点到定量实验验证的发展，拉瓦锡等人的实验提供了重要依据。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol1-knowledge-topic-0290-source-section-l3543-l3550-3bf6fa7832-promote-knowledge-topic-0290-source-section-l3543-l3550-3bf6fa7832-quiz-quiz-0290-source-section-l3543-l3550-3bf6fa7832",
