    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol1-knowledge-topic-0407-source-section-l5112-l5115-70b1ac3583-promote-knowledge-topic-0407-source-section-l5112-l5115-70b1ac3583-quiz-quiz-0407-source-section-l5112-l5115-70b1ac3583",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材指出不同地区家用燃料不同，要求关注燃料变迁、原因、影响以及使用注意事项。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0007-source-section-l66-l75-002391f54e-promote-knowledge-topic-0007-source-section-l66-l75-002391f54e-quiz-quiz-0007-source-section-l66-l75-002391f54e",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "答案是“铁的硬度和强度更适合承受切割、敲打等用途”。选择材料要看性质和用途。铁比铝更硬、更适合做受力工具，而铝较软。"
    },
    {
