      "field": "options[3]",
      "text": "合金的熔点常低于组成它的纯金属，可按用途选择材料"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0010-source-section-l99-l162-edcd46135a-promote-knowledge-topic-0010-source-section-l99-l162-edcd46135a-quiz-quiz-0010-source-section-l99-l162-edcd46135a",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "答案是“合金的熔点常低于组成它的纯金属，可按用途选择材料”。表中焊锡、伍德合金的熔点比相关纯金属低，说明合金组成改变会带来性能改变。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0015-source-section-l188-l233-e5a968cc18-promote-knowledge-topic-0015-source-section-l188-l233-e5a968cc18-quiz-quiz-0015-source-section-l188-l233-e5a968cc18",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "答案是“用品需要的强度、密度、熔点、耐腐蚀性等性能”。材料选择要让性质服务用途，例如飞机材料要轻而强，炊具要导热好。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0018-source-section-l240-l249-03fe6e1c85-promote-knowledge-topic-0018-source-section-l240-l249-03fe6e1c85-quiz-quiz-0018-source-section-l240-l249-03fe6e1c85",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "答案是“铝表面会生成致密的氧化铝薄膜，阻止继续氧化”。教材指出铝在空气中与氧气反应生成致密的氧化铝保护膜。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0039-source-section-l538-l541-3612c3a3a4-promote-knowledge-topic-0039-source-section-l538-l541-3612c3a3a4-quiz-quiz-0039-source-section-l538-l541-3612c3a3a4",
      "field": "options[2]",
      "text": "只使用最贵的金属材料"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0092-source-section-l1163-l1177-979015e717-promote-knowledge-topic-0092-source-section-l1163-l1177-979015e717-quiz-quiz-0092-source-section-l1163-l1177-979015e717",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材说明海水经储水池、蒸发池和结晶池，水分蒸发到一定程度后食盐晶体逐渐析出。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0149-ph-l1888-l1905-62315486eb-promote-knowledge-topic-0149-ph-l1888-l1905-62315486eb-quiz-quiz-0149-ph-l1888-l1905-62315486eb",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "教材说明酸碱度常用pH表示，常见范围通常为0到14，测定pH的简便方法是使用pH试纸。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0238-source-section-l2991-l3008-b608739989-promote-knowledge-topic-0238-source-section-l2991-l3008-b608739989-quiz-quiz-0238-source-section-l2991-l3008-b608739989",
      "field": "explanation",
      "text": "答案是“水、糖类、蛋白质、油脂、无机盐和维生素”。教材指出食物成分主要包括这六类营养物质。"
    },
    {
      "id": "textbook-rj-chemistry-grade9-2024-vol2-knowledge-topic-0250-source-section-l3154-l3157-41606c5602-promote-knowledge-topic-0250-source-section-l3154-l3157-41606c5602-quiz-quiz-0250-source-section-l3154-l3157-41606c5602",
